rangeFilter

public static <M,I> javax.swing.RowFilter<M,I> rangeFilter(RowFilters.RangeType type,
                                                           java.lang.Comparable lower,
                                                           java.lang.Comparable upper,
                                                           int... columns)
Returns a RowFilter which includes all entries which have at least one value in the specified range. The boundaries are swept internally, if lower > upper.

Parameters:
type - the RangeType to use in the comparison
lower - one boundery of the range
upper - the other boundary of the range
columns - the indices of the values to check. If not supplied all values are evaluated
Returns:
a RowFilter implementing the specified criteria
Throws:
java.lang.NullPointerException - if type, lower or upper is null
